data.description: Well maintained Harker Heights Gem a Verano Builder Executive edition.   The glorious open floor plan allows for all your hear desires for design, décor, and arrangement.  This 4bed 2bath modern home is a true beauty with an amazing chef inspired kitchen featuring custom wood kitchen cabinetry, granite countertops, travertine tile backsplash, and luxurious stainless-steel appliances including a nice oversize double sized stainless oven for the holidays.   The master suite has a spa like vibe with walk-In his and her closet, double vanities, a large soaking tub and a nice large shower.   The home is a great mix of modern elegance, comfort, and functionality.   This home is a great home for anyone wanting a well-built, comfortable place to call home in a wonderful neighborhood in Harker Heights.  The landscaping and curb appeal is on-point and looks amazing but yet it is still very easy to maintain and keep fresh.   The three additional bedrooms are quite spacious and offer a family a great footprint to function as a family unit.   The home also has additional upgrades like recessed lighting, solar screens, newer fence, new water heater, great roof and a sprinkler system.   The property is located near great shopping, parks, dining, and schools, making it an amazing choice for anyone wanting to live in an excellent Harker Heights neighborhood.
